</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-52">
where “<term>r</term>” is the position vector drawn from instantaneous axis of rotation. 
</para>
<para id="element-53">
<term> 5.</term> The magnitude of linear velocity i.e. speed of the particle is :
</para>
<para id="element-54">
